<h2 id="issues">Issues</h2>

<p>You can submit a bug report or a feature request through the <a href="https://github.com/spencer-mortensen/lens/issues">Issues</a> page.</p>

<h2 id="news">Announcements</h2>

<p>You can sign up for the announcement list if you’d like to hear about the really big announcements—such as how to upgrade through a backwards-compatibility break, or a new feature that could change the way you unit test.</p>

<p>Keep me informed when there is a big announcement:</p>

